---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import InnerPageHero from "../components/InnerPageHero.astro";
import { heroImages } from "../data/wixImages";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FAQ & Contact"
  description="Contact Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge Golf Club — hours, centennial FAQ, and guest information."
>
  <InnerPageHero eyebrow="We're here to help" title="FAQ & Contact" image={heroImages.home} />
  <div class="page-prose page-prose-wide">
    <div class="callout">
      <p><strong>Fairmont Jasper Park Lodge Golf Club</strong></p>
      <p>1 Old Lodge Road<br />Jasper, Alberta · Canada T0E 1E0</p>
      <p>
        <a href="tel:+17808526090">1 780 852 6090</a>
        <br />
        <a href="mailto:jpl.golfreservations@fairmont.com">jpl.golfreservations@fairmont.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>FAQs — centennial year</h2>
    <div class="faq">
      <details>
        <summary>When did the golf course reopen?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">
          <p>
            The club reopened Tuesday, July 1, 2025, launching centennial celebrations including a milestone anniversary July 17, 2025. Pre-season restoration (Jan–Jun 2025)
            included tree work to restore sightlines, select green resurfacing, and phased F&amp;B. The centennial season delivered 100 days of play for 100 years, with
            ongoing irrigation and enhancements. Legacy work continues 2025–2027 with bunkers, permanent venues, shelters, and landscaping.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Was the course affected by the 2024 wildfires?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">
          <p>
            Yes — significantly impacted, but with first responders, Parks Canada, and strategic irrigation, essential features were preserved. The reopening marks a
            new era of stewardship and excellence for Jasper.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Will all 18 holes be open?</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">
          <p>
            Yes — classic Thompson holes and revitalized features are planned to blend into the iconic layout. Some infrastructure work may continue seasonally with
            minimal disruption.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Winter hours</summary>
        <div class="faq-body">
          <p><strong>Course &amp; driving range:</strong> seasonal closure (e.g. effective mid-Oct — confirm annually).</p>
          <p><strong>Bear&apos;s Den (simulator):</strong> 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM daily.</p>
          <p><strong>Golf Pro Shop:</strong> 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM daily.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>

    <p>
      Follow <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fairmontJPL" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@fairmontJPL</a> for events and updates.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
